<p><a name="Logic.2C_mathematics.2C_methodology" id="Logic.2C_mathematics.2C_methodology"></a></p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline">Logic, mathematics, methodology</span></h3>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="multicol" style="background:transparent; width:100%;">
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="top">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Inference" title="Inference">Inference</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Abductive_reasoning" title="Abductive reasoning">Abductive reasoning</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Deductive_reasoning" title="Deductive reasoning">Deductive reasoning</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Inductive_reasoning" title="Inductive reasoning">Inductive reasoning</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
