<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> Crick, Francis (1994), <i>The Astonishing Hypothesis</i> <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0684194317" class="internal">ISBN 0-684-19431-7</a> p.20</li>
